        "code": "if not exist %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\ mkdir %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\\nif not exist %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\DBTools\\ mkdir %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\DBTools\\\nif not exist C:\\ServerSystem mkdir C:\\ServerSystem\n\nC:\\DayZSync\\wget.exe -nH --cut-dirs=2 -r --reject \u0022index.html*\u0022 http://www.gameservers.global/SyncSystem/Tools/ -P %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\\n\nping -n 1 127.0.0.1 \u003E nul\n\nC:\\DayZSync\\wget.exe -nH --cut-dirs=2 -r --reject \u0022index.html*\u0022 http://www.gameservers.global/SyncSystem/ConanExiles/DBTools/ -P %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\ 2\u003E NUL\n\nping -n 1 127.0.0.1 \u003E nul\n\nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\7za.exe 7za_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\winscp.com winscp_%ThisService_ServiceId%.com \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\winscp.exe winscp_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\ARKModCopy.exe ARKModCopy_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\FxUpdater.exe FxUpdater_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\mcrcon.exe mcrcon_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\PsInfo64.exe PsInfo64_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe\nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\UnRAR.exe UnRAR_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\wget.exe wget_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe \nren %ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\DBTools\\sqlite3.exe sqlite3_%ThisService_ServiceId%.exe\n\nif not exist C:\\ServerSystem\\Workshop\\steamcmd.exe xcopy /y/q/i \u0022%ThisService_RootDirectory%Tools\\Libraries\\steamcmd.exe\u0022 \u0022C:\\ServerSystem\\Workshop\\\u0022\n\nexit",
